Class MazeObject

java.lang.Object
MazeObject
public class MazeObject extends Object
MazeObject class, used in Level2, Level3, Minigame, to faciliate transfer of several types of information, like position, name, poisonous, etc

Course Info:

ICS4U0 with Krasteva, V.
